\v 16 N…ôkot…ôkeikei motol lan…ôha m…ôt…ôu-inu Nau…ôu…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôkot…ôkeikei motasim mot…ôhruahru m…ôt…ôu-inu I…ôu i…ôkasim m…ôhruahru.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:16  \xt Lev 11:44,45; 19:2; 20:7\x*   
\p
\v 17 It…ômah n…ôkot…ôtapu…ôh e nasirui…ôn o Uhg…®n u t…ôhmen m…ôm…ô in r…ôhat…ômah Tat…ô, m…ôt…ôu n…ôsotalui…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôtakil noli…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôt…ômimi r…ôfin, k…ôni in tatol …ôm…ô e noli…ôn i…ôt…ôm t…ôhmen-…ôhmen …ôm…ô. Tol lan…ôha, n…ôsotalui…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômah iap…®sp…®s m…®n …ôm…ô e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u. Sotoht…ôu-p…ôni…ôn noli…ôn m…®n r…ôhan. M…ôt…ôu nian n…ôut…ômi…ôg…ôh …ôhan…ôh e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u, on…ôkot…ôg…®n mot…®siai Uhg…®n e noli…ôn t…ôuv…®r m…®n r…ôhat…ômah.\x - \xo 1:17  \xt Rom 2:11; N…ôh 2:23\x*  
\v 18 N…ôkot…ôkeikei motol lan…ôha m…ôt…ôu-inu it…ômah n…ômot…ôhrun r…ôk…®s nati keikei i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôt…ôou r…ôk…®s it…ômah lan. Ot…ôt…ôl…®g-to e noli…ôn r…ôha n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhat…ômah aup…ôn i…ôt…ôm n…®p…ôt…®n t…®k…ô u t…ôms…®p…ôn o t…®p…®t…ômah m…®n. M…ôt…ôu Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…®s r…ôk…®s it…ômah e noli…ôn t…ôrah k…ôha. K…ôni Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsosi…ôn n…ôhmt…® n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhat…ômah e nati k…ôti r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni i…ôt…ôm ot…ôpan…®k…ô, t…ôhmen e s…®lf…ô m…®ne ai…ôn u kol t…ôtoraip-oraip,  
\v 19 m…ôt…ôu in t…ômos n…ôhmt…® t…ômah e n…®ra Kr…®sto i…ôt…ôm in nati keikei t…ôuv…®r p…®k ag…®n. Kr…®sto in t…ôhmen e n…ôt…® sipsip t…ôuv…®r i…ôt…ôm n…®m…®si…ôn u…ô n…ôrahi…ôn t…®k…ô ag…®n lan.\f + \fr 1:19  \ft E nian r…ôha Oltest…®m…®n, n…ôt…ômimi k…ômautol sakrifais k…ôm Uhg…®n o t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah m…®n e n…ôt…® sipsip m…®n i…ôt…ôm n…ôrahi…ôn t…®k…ô e lah. Afin e Eks 12:5.\f*\x - \xo 1:19  \xt U…ôk 20:28; Hip 9:12-14\x*   
\p
\v 20 Aup…ôn aup…ôn ag…®n, nian Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsol …ôhan…ôhi…ôn n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u, t…ôm…®t…ôp…®n r…ôk…®s Kr…®sto m…ôm…ô otol u…ôk …ôha. M…ôt…ôu r…ôueiu iu…ôk…®r o naunun nian, Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôpu in, m…ôm…ô otuva masiru e t…ômah.\x - \xo 1:20  \xt 2Tim 1:9-10\x*  
\v 21 K…ôni e natimnati m…®n …ôha Iesu t…ômol, it…ômah n…ôkot…ôhat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n, i…ôt…ôm t…ômosmi…ôg…ôh Iesu Kr…®sto e n…®m…®si…ôn, k…ôni m…ôf…ôri in m…ôf…ôn n…ôsan…ôni…ôn i…ôt…ôm t…ôhag…ôhag m…®ne n…®siai…ôn k…ôm in. K…ôni tol lan…ôha, n…ôkot…ôhat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n, k…ôni maut…ôl…ôhu=p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…ômah n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn lan.\x - \xo 1:21  \xt Jon 14:6; Rom 5:1-2\x*   
\p
\v 22 N…ômoteikuas e r…ôhat…ômah n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn t…®nuva m…®n…®vi m…®n r…ôk…®s m…ôt…ôu-inu n…ômot…ôt…ôu=p…ôn n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn. K…ôni o natimnati m…®n u, n…ôkotos nolkeikei…ôn p…ôhri…ôn t…ôtuva o t…ômah m…®n n…ôuvein. K…ôni tol lan…ôha, otolkeikei p…®k it…ômah m…®n e n…®kin p…ôhri…ôn.\x - \xo 1:22  \xt Jon 13:34; Rom 12:10\x*  
\v 23 Otol lan…ôha m…ôt…ôu-inu, n…ômotair vi r…ôk…®s m…®n, k…ôni n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn vi r…ôhat…ômah t…ôms…®s…®p…ôni…ôn o n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm ilah r…ôfin ok…ôpanohm…®s. M…ôt…ôu n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn vi u r…ôhat…ômah in ot…ôtat…®g naunun t…®k…ô, m…ôt…ôu-inu t…ôms…®p…ôn e n…ôghati…ôn k…ôti i…ôt…ôm t…ôt…ômi…ôg…ôh m…ôtat…®g naunun t…®k…ô, inu n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 24 Nau…ôu…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…ôt…ômimi r…ôfin kot…ôhmen e n…®mal…® n…®manuvehli,  
\q1 k…ôni n…ôuv…®ri…ôn r…ôfin r…ôhalah t…ôhmen …ôm…ô e n…ôug…®n…®gi …ôp…ôha e n…®kinati.  
