\v 22 Nau…ôu…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIn t…ôm…ôsoli…ôn t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah k…ôti,  
\q1 k…ôni in t…ôm…ôs…ôni…ôn n…ôghati…ôn eiu…ô m…®n nian k…ôti m…®ne.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:22  \xt Aes 53:9; Jon 8:46; 2Kor 5:21; 1Jon 3:5\x*   
\m
\v 23 Nian n…ôt…ômimi k…ômot…ôghati rah lan, m…ôt…ôu in t…ôm…ôsahi…ôn ilah. Nian in t…ôm…ôt…ôu nahm…ôi…ôn e n…®p…ôt…®n, m…ôt…ôu in t…ôm…ôs…ôni…ôn m…ôm…ô in otalp…®n n…®tai n…ôrahi…ôn. M…ôt…ôu in t…ôm…ôl…ôhu=p…ôn natimnati r…ôfin e n…ôhlm…® Uhg…®n i…ôt…ôm nian r…ôfin r…ôhan nakili…ôn in t…ôhruahru …ôm…ô.\x - \xo 2:23  \xt Aes 53:7; 1Pit…ô 3:9\x*  
