\c 3  
\s1 Noli…ôn t…ôuv…®r r…ôha i…ôrman m…®ne p…ôtan u k…ômuol mar…®t  
\m
\v 1 K…ôni e noli…ôn …ôhmen …ôm…ô r…ôha n…®siai…ôn I…ôrm…ôn…®g, it…ômah n…®p…ôtan n…ôkot…ôkeikei motol n…ôuia r…ôhat…ômah m…®n n…ôman m…ôt…ôu-inu o nati u. N…ôm…ô ilah k…ôsot…ôhat…ôt…ôi…ôn e n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôni r…ôhat…ômah noli…ôn t…ôuv…®r m…®n …ôm…ô okotiuvi=p…ôn r…ôhalah n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn o Uhg…®n. Noli…ôn t…ôuv…®r m…®n r…ôhat…ômah kot…ôhmen, motapir…ôk…®s n…ôm…ô n…ôut…ôghati k…ôm lah.\x - \xo 3:1  \xt Ef…ôs 5:22\x*  
